snippet.title: Tiny Witch Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: Tiny Witch is a small game about managing a "minion store". Activate spells, unlock new recipes, and prepare the best minions for your demanding (and sometimes aggressive) customers. https://store.steampowered.com/app/1740310/Tiny_Witch/ #indiegames #gamedev #steamnextfest
